{"tid":1761690,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(數據分析) 長者係咪真係傾向投俾建制派？","createTime":"2019-11-29T05:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T16:25:36.000Z","uid":336615,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5835fe05775992608cf037dab318c75116301a8","tid":1761690,"uid":336615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"呢場抗爭一直被理解是「年輕人」主導，亦流傳「藍絲廢老」等年齡定型的說法，小弟無無聊聊，嘗試用公開簡單數據測試一下年齡與區選的關係。今次用左統計上的相關系數（correlation），即係兩者之間既關係有幾強。<br />\n<br />\n統計分析主題：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">選區選民的年齡分佈與不同政治立場候選人得票率的關係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span></span><br />\n小弟是在社會研究界工作多年的small potato，經常偷懶但未至於被上司炒魷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，統計能力有限，如果分析有誤，望各位統計撚／社科撚見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">分析結果（非統計撚不用理會星星與p值）：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">綠色</span></span>即係果個年齡組別佔區內選民比例<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">越多</span></strong>，該政治立場嘅得票率<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">越高</span></strong>；<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紅色</span></span>即係果個年齡組別佔區內選民比例<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">越多</span></strong>，該政治立場嘅得票率<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">越低</span></strong>。<br />\n無顏色可以當無關係。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEQHOOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEQHOOV.jpg&h=7c1e830c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">初步解讀</span></span><br />\n以下是小弟對分析數據的初步解讀，純粹拋磚引玉，歡迎各位集思廣益：<br />\n<br />\n1）因為每區18至25歲嘅選民比例都差唔多(standard deviation太低)，分析結果睇黎都無咩意思，無得解讀。<br />\n<br />\n2）如果嗰區越多26至40歲選民，非建制得票率會越高。<br />\n<br />\n3）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果嗰區越多46至50歲選民，<span style=\"color: blue;\">建制</span>得票率會越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</strong></span>可能以前食正97移民潮條水（當年是24至28歲），依家上哂岸。<br />\n4）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果嗰區越多56至65歲選民，<span style=\"color: gold;\">非建制</span>得票率會越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。同坊間流傳的「收成期」或「藍絲廢老」講法有d唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>。可能因為呢班人見識過六四（當年是26至35歲），又可能佢地知道2018年5月10日由40位建制同3位泛民議員支持通過嘅《2018年撥款條例草案》入面嘅魔鬼細節提過：「把領取長者綜援的合資格年齡由 60 歲提高至 65 歲」。但通過左之後，建制派又話佢地不嬲都反對，即係「哎吔，唔小心睇漏左攪到通過左添」咁解。<br />\n（財政預算案：總目 170 - 社會福利署，p.797）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2018/chi/pdf/chead170.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2018%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Fchead170.pdf&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=7e3d2a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2018/chi/pdf/chead170.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n5）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果嗰區越多71歲或以上選民，<span style=\"color: blue;\">建制</span>得票率會越高。可能因為er...er...er..<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">數據來源：</span></span><br />\n小弟用左以下兩個資料作分析：<br />\n1）452個區議會選區登記選民的年齡組別及性別分佈(2019年)<br />\n政府在網上提供左每個區議會選區的已登記選民性別及年齡分佈，這次我只用年齡這個資料，換算成每區的年齡分佈百分比。例如屯門樂翠區的登記選民共有8,569人，18-20歲的登記選民男女合共205，佔2.39%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/statistic2019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fstatistic2019.html&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=16989910\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/statistic2019.html</a><br />\n2）立場新聞的2019 區議會選舉專頁：候選人的政治立場同票數<br />\n今次會以立場新聞的政治立場分類作準，將候選人分成「建制派」與「非建制派」，統計時分析有包括「不明確派系」，但因為樣本數太少（只有5個候選人勝出），亦不是每區都有灰色派候選人，所以結果略去不明確派候選人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://dce2019.thestandnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdce2019.thestandnews.com&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=a410712a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdce2019.thestandnews.com&h=944273d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://dce2019.thestandnews.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">For 統計撚／社科撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n統計分析樣本：區議會直選選區，共452個<br />\n變項(variable)：每區的選民年齡分佈百分比、同區建制派與非建制派候選人的得票百分比<br />\n分析工具：Pearson Correlation，Significance level設定在0.05"},{"pid":"e284136179b299cefb7c408a31fd33ae24bac9c1","tid":1761690,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"係三低選民，學歷低，智商低，EQ 低，"},{"pid":"9c321ffedaf35bbc2993c1f6dc5ffbe684de7063","tid":1761690,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n數據分析用心post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661143b34f16ebae979065c6f3d359a5d747ddc9","tid":1761690,"uid":293417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"aa015c5f654288d80d22e8c6b0aa2dc8a8fdc10b","tid":1761690,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5759c05e4d4922a534e75c488d41e95349e79bb9","tid":1761690,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"無一項大過0.3 個相關性唔高 even揾到sig."},{"pid":"298787b02ff40164463866afb252e0725ca70d1d","tid":1761690,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"80f96003d474664eec2cd13c78b9f59395c381ac","tid":1761690,"uid":336615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5759c05e4d4922a534e75c488d41e95349e79bb9","tid":1761690,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T07:29:52.000Z","msg":"無一項大過0.3 個相關性唔高 even揾到sig."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"相關性的確係唔高，亦都可能表示選民年齡比例既影響未必有一般想像中咁大"},{"pid":"e8d978b9a000eb8b34551fa9867492fd6a82474c","tid":1761690,"uid":336615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c321ffedaf35bbc2993c1f6dc5ffbe684de7063","tid":1761690,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n數據分析用心post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:25:36.000Z","msg":"多謝支持呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}